00:34:46,542 --> 00:34:48,042
我猜是吧
I guess, yeah.

558
00:34:49,083 --> 00:34:50,958
我那不还没修完车呢么
I just haven't done this stuff in a while.

559
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,208
咱俩一块进去
Makes two of us.

560
00:35:09,458 --> 00:35:10,750
嘿，你想在这儿玩吗？
Hey, so, do you just want to hang out here?

561
00:35:10,792 --> 00:35:11,917
我去拿点喝的
I'll get us something to drink.

562
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,042
好
Yeah.

563
00:35:23,250 --> 00:35:24,792
要不跟我一块来吧？
Or come with me?

564
00:35:25,375 --> 00:35:26,417
我跟你一块去
I'll come with you.

565
00:35:37,292 --> 00:35:38,417
嘿，他在那呢
Hey, there he is!

566
00:35:38,542 --> 00:35:39,625
嘿，朋友们
Hi, guys...

567
00:35:39,708 --> 00:35:41,083
抱歉认错人了
Sorry to bother you,

568
00:35:41,125 --> 00:35:42,417
我们的朋友
it's just we used to know someone

569
00:35:42,500 --> 00:35:43,750
跟你这个朋友长得很像
who looked just like your friend here.

570
00:35:44,333 --> 00:35:46,000
我叫泰萨，很高兴认识你
I'm Tessa. It's nice to meet you.

571
00:35:46,042 --> 00:35:47,542
如果你能让他从这出去
If you're the one that got him out of the house,

572
00:35:47,625 --> 00:35:48,750
那就也很高兴认识你
it's good to meet you, too.

573
00:35:48,792 --> 00:35:50,125
大学怎么样？
How's college?

574
00:35:50,375 --> 00:35:51,750
你甚至都不用假装什么都学
You don't even have to pretend to learn anything.

575
00:35:51,833 --> 00:35:53,750
你也应该试试。是啊，我会的，有机会吧
You should try it. Yeah, I will, sometime.

576
00:35:58,375 --> 00:35:59,375
你还喝这个吗？
Are you drinking this?

577
00:35:59,458 --> 00:36:00,458
喝呀……
Yeah, actually...

578
00:36:06,042 --> 00:36:08,083
嗯，我觉得挺好，突然闯到一个聚会上去
Yeah, it's good, I think, just to pop in to parties like that.

579
00:36:08,167 --> 00:36:10,208
我不想因为待得太久而招人讨厌，你呢？
Don't want to outstay a welcome, do you?

580
00:36:10,292 --> 00:36:13,583
你在聚会上还挺受欢迎，你应该多出来参加这种聚会
You got a pretty big one there. You should get out more.

581
00:36:13,667 --> 00:36:17,458
他们并不介意我进去，是吧？
Well, then they wouldn't care when I walked in, would they?

582
00:36:17,542 --> 00:36:19,000
那个姑娘欺负过你？
Did that girl hurt you?

583
00:36:19,125 --> 00:36:20,583
别的方式欺负的我
Other way round.

584
00:36:20,667 --> 00:36:22,333
她一拳打到我下巴上了，可疼了
I caught her fist a good one with my chin,

585
00:36:22,417 --> 00:36:25,667
然后我就用鼻子挡她的膝盖
then whacked her right in the knee with my nose.

586
00:36:26,583 --> 00:36:27,917
你还真得小心点
You need to be careful.

587
00:36:28,042 --> 00:36:29,333
用不着
No, I don't.

588
00:36:30,250 --> 00:36:31,958
就是这么回事
That's the thing.

589
00:36:34,042 --> 00:36:35,250
你到家了
Here you go then.

590
00:36:35,375 --> 00:36:36,625
你这是什么意思？
How do you mean?

591
00:36:37,167 --> 00:36:38,708
你到家了。不，瞎说，不行
This is you. No, bollocks, no way.

592
00:36:38,792 --> 00:36:39,958
我送你到家门口
I'll walk you to your door.

593
00:36:40,042 --> 00:36:41,417
不用了吧？-当然用，没事
Are you sure? -Yeah, of course, no trouble.

594
00:36:44,125 --> 00:36:45,208
看
See?

595
00:36:48,333 --> 00:36:49,792
谢谢你
Thank you.

596
00:37:48,250 --> 00:37:49,375
嘿
Hey.

597
00:37:51,208 --> 00:37:52,333
你好
Hello.

598
00:37:53,167 --> 00:37:54,625
你掉了五块钱
You dropped a fiver.

599
00:37:54,708 --> 00:37:55,708
什么？
What?

600
00:37:55,833 --> 00:37:58,125
五块钱，你掉的
That fiver. You dropped it.

601
00:37:58,958 --> 00:38:00,625
那不是我的
That's not mine.

602
00:38:00,708 --> 00:38:02,167
我看见它从你兜里掉出来的
I saw it come out of your pocket.

603
00:38:03,333 --> 00:38:05,292
真得吗？-可不
Really? - Yeah.

604
00:38:06,250 --> 00:38:08,042
因为我当时正往那看呢
'Cause I was looking.

605
00:38:11,958 --> 00:38:14,250
好吧，谢谢
Okay, well, thanks.

606
00:38:24,583 --> 00:38:26,208
太牛逼了！绝对的
That was so cool. It totally was.

607
00:38:26,292 --> 00:38:28,750
我们像真正的窃贼一样牛逼！你那双勾人的眼睛太厉害了
We rock as criminals. That flirty eye thing you were doing.

608
00:38:28,833 --> 00:38:31,417
你拿卡的时间也恰到好处
What about you nipping in there with the perfect timing?

609
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:32,542
那咱们现在干吗？
So now what?

610
00:38:32,583 --> 00:38:34,042
现在咱们去取点钱然后去个聚会
Now we get some cash out and party.

611
00:38:34,083 --> 00:38:35,458
用这卡取？-是的
With the card? -Right.

612
00:38:35,542 --> 00:38:36,750
好吧，密码是什么？
Okay. What's the number?

613
00:38:36,875 --> 00:38:38,125
你什么意思？
What do you mean?

614
00:38:39,208 --> 00:38:40,500
你没看见密码吗？
Didn't you see the number?

615
00:38:40,583 --> 00:38:42,125
没有哇，我当时正忙着用眼睛电他呢
No, I was doing the flirty eye thing.

616
00:38:42,208 --> 00:38:43,417
我只管拿卡
I was nipping in there.

617
00:38:43,958 --> 00:38:45,458
咱俩这盗贼当的太屎了
We suck as criminals.

618
00:38:46,167 --> 00:38:48,583
也许这样最好。那哥们看上去没事
Probably best.The guy seemed all right.

619
00:38:48,667 --> 00:38:49,958
要不咱俩试试再把卡还给他
Maybe we should try and give his card back.

620
00:38:50,042 --> 00:38:51,042
怎么还？
And how are we going to do that?

621
00:38:51,083 --> 00:38:52,667
希望我没打断你们，回来！
Not interrupting anything,am I? Get...

622
00:39:15,542 --> 00:39:17,333
泰萨……干吗？
Tessa...What?

623
00:39:17,417 --> 00:39:19,083
那张卡。-卡怎么？
The card. -What about it?

624
00:39:19,167 --> 00:39:20,750
还给他
Give it back to him!

625
00:39:31,583 --> 00:39:33,958
斯科特老耍酷，我知道他对我着迷了
Scott plays it cool.I know he's crazy about me.

626
00:39:34,042 --> 00:39:35,375
你怎么知道？
How'd you know?

627
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:36,833
因为他是男的
Because he's a guy.

628
00:39:36,917 --> 00:39:38,292
我信你
I'll take your word for it.

629
00:39:38,375 --> 00:39:40,125
那你说他昨天晚上干吗不给我打电话？
So, why didn't he call me last night?

630
00:39:40,208 --> 00:39:41,792
小邹，有个事我想跟你说
Zo, there's something I need to tell you.

631
00:39:41,917 --> 00:39:43,458
咱先把这一票干完
Let's get this done first.

632
00:39:43,542 --> 00:39:45,458
记住，在商店里偷东西靠得全是自信
Remember, shoplifting's all about confidence.

633
00:39:45,542 --> 00:39:47,875
抬头挺胸，拿起来放进包里
Walk tall, pick and pocket.

634
00:39:47,958 --> 00:39:50,375
进去之后咱俩分开行动
In there, we go in separate.

635
00:39:50,875 --> 00:39:51,875
为什么不能在一起？
Why not together?

636
00:39:51,958 --> 00:39:53,167
在一块更可以，走吧
More suspicious. Go on.

637
00:39:55,917 --> 00:39:57,458
好吧
Right.

638
00:40:31,375 --> 00:40:33,625
泰萨？泰萨·斯科特？
Tessa? Tessa Scott?

639
00:40:33,875 --> 00:40:35,333
不，不是我
No. Sorry.

640
00:40:35,375 --> 00:40:36,875
就是你
It is you.

641
00:40:37,042 --> 00:40:39,625
你还记得我们俩吗？高中的时候
Don't you remember us? From school.

642
00:40:42,292 --> 00:40:43,458
哦，是啊
Oh, yeah.

643
00:40:43,750 --> 00:40:45,167
你11岁的时候转学了，是吧？
You left in Year 11,didn't you?

644
00:40:45,708 --> 00:40:46,833
十岁
Ten.

645
00:40:48,042 --> 00:40:52,208
你现在怎么样了？还在进行化疗吗？
So how's it going? Are you still having all that treatment?

646
00:40:54,125 --> 00:40:55,292
不治了
Not anymore.

647
00:40:55,583 --> 00:40:56,667
这么说你好点了？
So you're better?

648
00:40:57,208 --> 00:40:58,250
没有
No.

649
00:41:02,417 --> 00:41:03,750
你们想干吗呀？
What do you two want?

650
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,958
嘿，邹逸，你帮她购物吗？
Hi, Zoey. You helping her shop?

651
00:41:07,917 --> 00:41:09,292
走吧？-好
Are you ready to go? -Yeah.

652
00:41:09,375 --> 00:41:11,208
你跟斯科特·雷蒙德约会，是真的吗？
Is it true you've been seeing Scott Redmond?

653
00:41:14,625 --> 00:41:16,250
关你屁事？- 你认识他吗？
What's it to you? -Do you know him?

654
00:41:16,333 --> 00:41:17,333
行了，走吧
All right, let's go.

655
00:41:17,375 --> 00:41:18,458
大家都认识他
Everybody knows him.

656
00:41:18,542 --> 00:41:21,417
半小时前他跟我姐姐出去了
He went out with my sister for about half an hour.

657
00:41:22,250 --> 00:41:23,792
是么？
Is that right?

658
00:41:24,167 --> 00:41:26,125
我还得去选我葬礼的邀请卡呢
I have to go collect the invites for my funeral.

659
00:41:26,583 --> 00:41:28,208
真的？-是啊
Really? -Yeah.

660
00:41:28,292 --> 00:41:29,500
我还得去整理我的悼词
I also need to sort out the readings.

661
00:41:29,583 --> 00:41:31,958
确保那不是一首破诗，这些都得在我死前弄完
Make sure it's not that bloody poem. It's been done to death.

662
00:41:32,250 --> 00:41:33,333
放开我
Let go of me.

663
00:41:33,417 --> 00:41:35,875
她们都是傻逼，小邹，她们什么都不知道
They're idiots, Zo. They don't know anything.

664
00:41:35,958 --> 00:41:37,250
我知道
I know.

665
00:41:38,167 --> 00:41:39,208
我得去找他去
I have to go find him.

666
00:41:39,792 --> 00:41:40,875
现在？
NOW?

667
00:41:41,333 --> 00:41:43,708
是啊，对不起，我得走了
Yeah. I'm sorry. I need to go.

668
00:41:48,208 --> 00:41:49,458
嘿！
Hey!

669
00:42:07,333 --> 00:42:08,958
还有一个，把她也抓住！
Another one! Stop her too!

670
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:16,375
抓住了
Gotcha.

671
00:42:23,500 --> 00:42:24,917
坐下
Sit down.

672
00:42:25,708 --> 00:42:27,500
把兜里东西都掏出来 
Empty your pockets.

673
00:42:34,083 --> 00:42:37,083
好了，我管这些叫证据，你知道么？
Well, I'd call that evidence, wouldn't you?

674
00:42:37,917 --> 00:42:40,417
姓名，住址，父母的电话
Name. Address. Parents' phone numbers.

675
00:42:40,833 --> 00:42:42,167
别给我爸打电话
Don't call my dad.

676
00:42:42,292 --> 00:42:43,667
我们有两个选择
We have a choice.

677
00:42:44,250 --> 00:42:46,458
要不然给你爸打电话，要不然就报警
We can call him, or we can call the police.

678
00:42:46,583 --> 00:42:48,958
报警吧，每次都是报警
The police, every time.

679
00:42:49,667 --> 00:42:52,792
我跟门外那个人说我能处理这个，不过如果你……
Now, I told that guy out there I'd handle it, and if you...

680
00:42:52,875 --> 00:42:54,208
听着……
Listen...

681
00:43:00,417 --> 00:43:02,083
这是一个植入式经脉输液口
This is a portacath.

682
00:43:04,208 --> 00:43:06,500
化疗透析用的
It's an access disk for medical treatments.

683
00:43:06,917 --> 00:43:09,333
我得了急性淋巴细胞白血病
I have acute lymphoblastic leukemia.

684
00:43:09,875 --> 00:43:11,708
请你把衣服穿好
Please put your shirt back on.

685
00:43:12,167 --> 00:43:14,417
你知道什么叫急性淋巴细胞白血病吗？
Do you know what acute lymphoblastic leukemia is?

686
00:43:14,583 --> 00:43:16,292
不，恐怕我不知道
No, I'm afraid I don't.

687
00:43:16,667 --> 00:43:17,833
就是癌症
It's cancer.

688
00:43:25,375 --> 00:43:27,708
那我还是得给你爸打电话
I still have to call your dad.

689
00:43:29,500 --> 00:43:32,667
还有你，你什么借口啊？
And you, what's your excuse?

690
00:43:33,625 --> 00:43:35,375
她都偷什么了？
What did she take?

691
00:43:36,125 --> 00:43:38,708
蓝条家庭验孕棒
One Clearblue Home Pregnancy Test.

692
00:43:54,333 --> 00:43:57,708
这也在你的列表上吗？在商店偷东西？
Was this on the list? Shoplifting?

693
00:44:04,625 --> 00:44:06,375
你这是干吗呀？泰萨？
What are you doing, Tessa?

694
00:44:06,583 --> 00:44:07,583
你这是干吗？
What are you doing?

695
00:44:07,667 --> 00:44:09,000
尽我所能，尽快实现我这些愿望
As much as I can.As fast as I can.

696
00:44:09,917 --> 00:44:11,417
我希望你停下来
I wish you'd stop.

697
00:44:11,792 --> 00:44:13,250
你愿意让我下半辈子
You'd prefer I spend the rest of my life

698
00:44:13,292 --> 00:44:14,708
裹着毯子蜷在沙发里
huddled in a blanket on the sofa,

699
00:44:14,750 --> 00:44:16,250
头垂在你的肩膀上吗
with my head on your shoulder.

700
00:44:18,083 --> 00:44:20,125
是，我愿意，你要责怪我吗？
Yeah, I would.Can you blame me?

701
00:44:22,458 --> 00:44:23,958
是的，我愿意
Yes, I would.

702
00:44:28,250 --> 00:44:32,042
我的意思是，我的意思是我喜欢强壮的女人
My point is... Well, my point is, I like a strong woman.

703
00:44:32,125 --> 00:44:33,417
你一直喜欢被抱上床的感觉吧
You've always wanted to be carried to bed.

704
00:44:33,583 --> 00:44:35,542
我一直就想被人抱上床
I have always wanted to be carried to bed.

705
00:44:35,625 --> 00:44:37,792
我不喜欢什么呢，把一个
What I don't do, is bring to a mate's party

706
00:44:37,875 --> 00:44:40,875
公认的，完美的，显形的，年轻精灵术士带到哥们的聚会上去
an, admittedly perfectly formed, young pixie warlock.

707
00:44:41,125 --> 00:44:42,375
她可不是什么术士
Yeah, she's isn't a warlock.

708
00:44:42,458 --> 00:44:43,667
我意思是，你不能到处去
I mean you can't just go around

709
00:44:43,708 --> 00:44:45,208
找人打架
starting fights every which way

710
00:44:45,292 --> 00:44:46,583
而且到处砸东西吧（手机：往右看）
and shaking things up like that.

711
00:44:51,625 --> 00:44:53,458
显然你可以那么干
Apparently you can.

712
00:45:04,917 --> 00:45:06,375
你到这来干吗？
What are you doing here?

713
00:45:07,167 --> 00:45:08,833
我都跟踪你一整天了
I've been stalking you all day.

714
00:45:09,042 --> 00:45:11,917
我才刚刚鼓起勇气现身的
I only just now plucked up the courage to reveal myself.

715
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:13,083
是吗？
Really?

716
00:45:13,875 --> 00:45:15,000
不是
No.

717
00:45:17,708 --> 00:45:20,208
我爸在绿色食品店买东西呢，他可能会开车经过这儿
My dad's in the health food store.He could drive past.

718
00:45:24,042 --> 00:45:25,375
能在见到你的朋友们真好
It's nice to see your mates again.

719
00:45:28,125 --> 00:45:30,708
是啊，永远那么兴奋
Yeah. Always a pleasure.

720
00:45:38,500 --> 00:45:41,708
好了，怎么回头见吧
Well, I'll see you around, maybe.

721
00:45:41,833 --> 00:45:43,250
好的
Sure, yeah.

722
00:45:48,333 --> 00:45:50,000
我知道你还看着我呢
I know you're looking.

723
00:45:50,792 --> 00:45:52,083
我没看
I'm not looking.

724
00:45:53,083 --> 00:45:54,292
瞎说
Liar.

725
00:46:02,208 --> 00:46:04,917
也许你该考虑一下回去上学
Perhaps you should think about going back to school.

726
00:46:05,042 --> 00:46:07,083
把你的生活搞得正常一点
A bit of normality in your life.

727
00:46:07,167 --> 00:46:09,333
我不想回去上学
I'm not going back to school.

728
00:46:09,417 --> 00:46:11,708
癌症晚期应该振作一些
There's got to be some perks to terminal illness.

729
00:46:15,333 --> 00:46:16,792
我烦死你了吧？
I'm killing you, right?

730
00:46:18,083 --> 00:46:19,333
每天都是
Every day.

731
00:46:23,250 --> 00:46:24,625
看着点，哥们
Watch out, mate.

732
00:46:25,542 --> 00:46:27,125
臭傻逼
Bloody idiot.

733
00:46:29,708 --> 00:46:31,375
这家伙要干吗？
What's this guy up to?

734
00:46:46,167 --> 00:46:48,792
泰萨，你干吗去啊？泰萨？
Tessa, where are you going? Tessa?

735
00:46:52,417 --> 00:46:54,083
泰萨！
Tessa!

736
00:47:34,667 --> 00:47:36,208
骑摩托车的感觉
That was good.

737
00:47:36,708 --> 00:47:38,625
真不错
A ride on a motorbike.

738
00:47:39,208 --> 00:47:41,167
这事应该在我的癌症清单上
Should have been on my list.

739
00:47:41,250 --> 00:47:43,042
都什么呀？说一个听听
What is? Name one.

740
00:47:44,208 --> 00:47:45,375
出名
Fame.

741
00:47:47,458 --> 00:47:48,917
你要多出名啊？
How famous do you want to be?

