What are you doing here?

931
01:02:49,542 --> 01:02:51,417
你爸和卡尔到处找你，你到哪去了？
Dad and Cal are looking for you. Where have you been?

932
01:02:52,167 --> 01:02:54,083
咱们改天再聊吧
We'll have to talk about it some other time.

933
01:02:55,000 --> 01:02:56,125
为什么？
Why?

934
01:02:58,000 --> 01:02:59,917
因为我得去赴一个约会
'Cause I've got a date.

935
01:03:04,333 --> 01:03:05,625
对，她回来了
Yeah. She's here.

936
01:03:24,958 --> 01:03:27,458
今晚不行，今晚可不能犯病
Not tonight. Please, not tonight.

937
01:03:27,542 --> 01:03:30,583
行了，我跟你爸说了，我告诉他不用担心，他……
Okay, I've called your father. I've told him not to worry. He's going...

938
01:03:31,792 --> 01:03:33,750
我的天呐！-只是流鼻血而已
Oh, my God. -It's just a nosebleed.

939
01:03:34,208 --> 01:03:36,625
不是吧，你的血都快流干了，泰萨，我……
No, it's pumping out of you. Tessa, I...

940
01:03:37,083 --> 01:03:39,000
我该怎么办？-我不知道……
What should I do? -I don't know...

941
01:03:39,083 --> 01:03:40,833
给，拿这毛巾
Here, take a towel.

942
01:03:41,333 --> 01:03:44,000
坐下，捏捏鼻子什么的
Sit down. Pinch your nose or something.

943
01:03:46,500 --> 01:03:48,458
哦，你得去医院
Oh, you need to go to hospital.

944
01:03:48,750 --> 01:03:50,750
一会血就不流了。我得给你爸打电话
It'll stop in a minute. I'm calling your father.

945
01:03:50,833 --> 01:03:53,083
我该给你爸打电话吗？我该怎么办啊
Should I call your father? I don't know what to do.

946
01:03:53,167 --> 01:03:54,917
告诉我该干什么！ -给我拿点冰块来
Tell me what to do! -Just get me some ice.

947
01:03:55,375 --> 01:03:57,000
什么？ -冰块！
What? -Ice!

948
01:03:57,083 --> 01:03:59,417
最好是一带冻豌豆
A bag of frozen peas would be best.

949
01:04:00,583 --> 01:04:02,458
对，冻豌豆
Right. Frozen peas.

950
01:04:10,042 --> 01:04:13,250
这有甜玉米，甜玉米行吗？
There's sweet corn. Is sweet corn okay?

951
01:04:14,292 --> 01:04:15,417
哦，天呐
Oh, Jesus.

952
01:04:15,583 --> 01:04:16,958
你还是带我去医院吧
You have to take me to hospital.

953
01:04:17,500 --> 01:04:19,833
我不行，泰萨，我觉得应该让你爸带你去
I can't, Tessa. I think your father should do this.

954
01:04:19,917 --> 01:04:20,958
来不及了
There isn't time.

955
01:04:21,042 --> 01:04:22,042
好吧
Okay.

956
01:04:22,792 --> 01:04:24,583
是的，叫辆救护车，谢谢，快点，快点！
Yes. Ambulance, please. Quickly. Quickly!

957
01:04:27,542 --> 01:04:28,917
那是谁？-不
Who is it? -No.

958
01:04:29,000 --> 01:04:30,500
那是谁？-他不能……
Who is it? -He can't...

959
01:04:30,583 --> 01:04:32,083
我需要帮助。-别让他进来
I need help. -Don't let him in.

960
01:04:32,125 --> 01:04:33,167
不行，我需要帮手
No, I need help.

961
01:04:33,208 --> 01:04:34,375
他不能看见我这样
He can't see me like this!

962
01:04:34,417 --> 01:04:37,125
泰丝，我自己干不了，我需要帮手
Tess, I can't do this on my own. I need help.

963
01:04:58,583 --> 01:04:59,625
进来
Coming.

964
01:04:59,708 --> 01:05:01,917
帮我把她抬到楼下去
Help me get her downstairs.

965
01:05:05,250 --> 01:05:06,875
快点，你帮不帮忙？
Come on. Are you gonna help?

966
01:05:07,042 --> 01:05:08,667
让他出去，求你了
Get him out! Please.

967
01:05:08,750 --> 01:05:10,750
好吧，你走吧，我们能处理，走
All right, just go.We can manage. Go.

968
01:05:18,917 --> 01:05:20,167
给你拿着这个好吗？
Would you hold that?

969
01:05:21,292 --> 01:05:22,750
谢谢你
Thank you.

970
01:05:29,000 --> 01:05:30,125
亚当
Adam.

971
01:05:32,792 --> 01:05:34,792
她肯定会很渴，她流了好多血
She must be thirsty. She's lost so much blood.

972
01:05:34,875 --> 01:05:36,417
要不要给她喝点水？用不用？
Should she have some water? Should she?

973
01:05:36,500 --> 01:05:38,667
还是让医生来看看吧，好吗？
Let's see what the doctor says, all right.

974
01:05:40,125 --> 01:05:41,917
很好，到这来
Good. Here you are.

975
01:05:44,292 --> 01:05:47,667
好，以前有没有血小板减少的症状？
Right. Any signs of thrombocytopenia before today?

976
01:05:48,625 --> 01:05:50,542
孩儿她妈？孩儿她妈？
Mum? Mum?

977
01:05:50,667 --> 01:05:52,583
抱歉，问我呐？
Sorry, me?

978
01:05:52,625 --> 01:05:54,208
她有没有抱怨过头疼？
Has she complained of a headache?

979
01:05:54,292 --> 01:05:56,083
你有没有注意到什么她注射过毒品？
Have you noticed any pinprick bruising?

980
01:05:56,167 --> 01:05:57,625
说实话，我没注意
I didn't look, to be honest.

981
01:05:57,708 --> 01:05:59,792
她最后一次输血是什么时候？
When was the last platelet transfusion?

982
01:05:59,875 --> 01:06:01,958
我不知道，我可以找人问问
I'm not sure. I can try...I can try and find out.

983
01:06:02,750 --> 01:06:04,750
她最近有没有用过什么阿司匹林之类的药？
Has she used any aspirin products recently?

984
01:06:04,833 --> 01:06:06,083
我不知道，我不知道
I don't know. I don't...

985
01:06:06,167 --> 01:06:08,417
对不起，这些问题我一个都答不上来
I'm sorry. I don't know the answers to any of these questions.

986
01:06:08,458 --> 01:06:11,000
我最后一次血小板输血是五月十八号
My last platelet transfusion was May 18th.

987
01:06:11,083 --> 01:06:13,208
好的，谢谢你，别说话了
Okay, thank you. Don't talk.

988
01:06:13,292 --> 01:06:17,250
孩儿她妈，过来，握住你女儿的手
Mum, get yourself round here, and hold your daughter's hand.

989
01:06:17,417 --> 01:06:21,167
好，捏你妈妈的手，一次是：是，两次是：否
Okay. Squeeze your mum's hand once for yes, twice for no.

990
01:06:21,250 --> 01:06:23,292
明白了吗？别说话
Understand? Don't talk.

991
01:06:23,667 --> 01:06:24,792
是
Yes.

992
01:06:24,875 --> 01:06:28,167
有没有血小板减少症？头疼？瘀伤？
Any signs of thrombocytopenia? Headaches? Bruising?

993
01:06:28,792 --> 01:06:29,875
否
No.

994
01:06:29,958 --> 01:06:33,250
阿司匹林类药？宝治灵？替钾？消炎药？
Aspirin products? Bonjela? Teejel? Anti-inflammatories?

995
01:06:33,292 --> 01:06:34,417
没有，一个都没有
No, none of those. No.

996
01:06:34,500 --> 01:06:35,583
好
Good.

997
01:06:35,875 --> 01:06:37,875
现在，恐怕我们要用灼伤性方式给你的鼻子消毒
Now I'm afraid we're going to need to cauterize your nose.

998
01:06:38,250 --> 01:06:40,458
以前做过灼伤性消毒吗？-是的，她说做过
Have you been cauterized before? -Yes, she has.

999
01:06:40,542 --> 01:06:42,292
好的，我们检查一下你的血小板
Okay. We'll check your platelets,

1000
01:06:42,375 --> 01:06:45,250
然后你需要输至少两个单位的血小板
and then you're going to need at least a couple of units.

1001
01:06:45,333 --> 01:06:48,083
今晚会很难过，不过你明天一早就可以回家了
A rough night, but you'll be back home tomorrow.

1002
01:06:49,375 --> 01:06:51,458
我们知道病症所在了
We got there in the end.

1003
01:07:13,417 --> 01:07:17,292
大夫说是晚期鼻子出血，你知道，严重的那种
They said it was a posterior nosebleed, the...You know, the bad kind.

1004
01:07:20,208 --> 01:07:24,125
他们给她的鼻子做了血管……
They had to pack her nose with vaso...

1005
01:07:25,042 --> 01:07:26,292
血管收缩术
Vasoconstrictive.

1006
01:07:26,375 --> 01:07:28,542
对，血管收缩药
Yeah, vasoconstrictive agents.

1007
01:07:28,583 --> 01:07:31,917
在那之前，输了两个单位的血，还做了血小板计数
And before they transfused in two units, they did a platelet count.

1008
01:07:33,042 --> 01:07:34,167
还有呢？
And?

1009
01:07:35,000 --> 01:07:36,042
稳定了
Stable.

1010
01:07:46,125 --> 01:07:47,625
你干得不错
You did well.

1011
01:07:52,208 --> 01:07:54,125
我在这，你要是有事的话可以走了
I'm here, you can go now if you want.

1012
01:07:57,375 --> 01:07:58,458
我能留下吗？
Can I stay?

1013
01:08:03,333 --> 01:08:04,583
当然了
Yeah.

1014
01:08:49,417 --> 01:08:51,083
你感觉怎么样？
How are you feeling?

1015
01:08:52,042 --> 01:08:53,417
困
Sleepy...

1016
01:08:54,000 --> 01:08:55,417
谢谢你能陪我
Thank you for being there.

1017
01:08:57,625 --> 01:09:01,000
我真是被你吓坏了，还有你的男朋友
It was a bit of a shock. For your boy, too.

1018
01:09:02,333 --> 01:09:03,792
我能理解
It was understandable.

1019
01:09:10,083 --> 01:09:11,708
那孩子真挺招人喜欢的，跟奶酥似的
He's a hot buttered biscuit, that one.

1020
01:09:14,292 --> 01:09:16,750
是啊，我也是这么形容他的
Yeah, that's exactly how I'd describe him.

1021
01:09:17,042 --> 01:09:18,833
你会怎么跟他说？
What would you say?

1022
01:09:21,208 --> 01:09:24,083
他要没跟我在一起，我就随便编个理由
When he's not with me, I think I've made him up.

1023
01:09:26,625 --> 01:09:28,667
他没再打电话或者跟到医院去吧？
He didn't call or come after us, or anything?

1024
01:09:30,625 --> 01:09:31,833
没有
No.

1025
01:09:33,750 --> 01:09:35,625
也许我应该骗他
Maybe I did make him up.

1026
01:09:39,708 --> 01:09:41,000
天呐
Good God.

1027
01:09:42,333 --> 01:09:43,375
怎么了？
What?

1028
01:09:43,583 --> 01:09:45,500
看那，在桥上
There, on the bridge.

1029
01:09:52,625 --> 01:09:54,083
真奇怪
That's odd.

1030
01:10:01,250 --> 01:10:02,917
到处都是你的名字，泰萨！
You're everywhere, Tessa!

1031
01:10:21,667 --> 01:10:23,083
是他干的
He's done it.

1032
01:10:25,625 --> 01:10:27,583
他把我的名字写得到处都是
He's put my name in the world.

1033
01:10:38,792 --> 01:10:40,917
杂耍棍！你给我买了杂耍滚！
Juggling clubs! You brought me juggling clubs!

1034
01:10:41,583 --> 01:10:42,792
生日快乐！
Happy birthday.

1035
01:10:42,875 --> 01:10:43,958
你会玩吗？
Can you do these?

1036
01:10:44,333 --> 01:10:45,667
会，会一点
Yeah. A bit, yeah.

1037
01:10:45,750 --> 01:10:47,417
你要是想学我待会教你
I'll help you practice later if you want.

1038
01:10:47,833 --> 01:10:49,542
爸爸，亚当能留下吃晚饭吗？
Dad, can Adam stay for dinner?

1039
01:10:49,708 --> 01:10:50,750
不行
No.

1040
01:10:51,458 --> 01:10:52,542
妈妈
Mum...

1041
01:10:52,625 --> 01:10:53,792
我又不住在这，说了不算吧？
I don't live here, do I?

1042
01:10:54,542 --> 01:10:55,750
谢谢你
Thank you.

1043
01:10:55,833 --> 01:10:56,958
不过还是让他留下吧
But let him stay.

1044
01:10:57,458 --> 01:10:58,917
你们串通好了的
It's a conspiracy.

1045
01:11:00,792 --> 01:11:02,958
好吧，我表演个魔术
All right,on with the magic show.

1046
01:11:03,042 --> 01:11:04,125
挑一张牌
Pick a card.

1047
01:11:06,708 --> 01:11:07,750
红桃五
Five of hearts.

1048
01:11:08,042 --> 01:11:09,083
不是
No.

1049
01:11:10,250 --> 01:11:11,625
总有一天我能猜出来
One day I'll get the right one,

1050
01:11:11,750 --> 01:11:13,125
你们都是废物
and you'll all crap yourselves.

1051
01:11:13,250 --> 01:11:15,875
哦，好哇，你现在都能说脏话啦？
Oh, nice. He's allowed to say that, is he?

1052
01:11:15,958 --> 01:11:17,708
只能说“废物”
It's only "crap."

1053
01:11:42,417 --> 01:11:44,375
好了，又有一件事可以从清单上划掉了
Well, that's another one to cross off the list.

1054
01:11:49,042 --> 01:11:50,750
你那清单还剩多少？
How's the list going?

1055
01:11:51,542 --> 01:11:55,250
剩下的我觉得都不重要了
Things I thought mattered don't matter so much anymore.

1056
01:11:56,875 --> 01:11:59,625
你怎么样？有什么计划吗？
How about you? Got anything you wanna put up there?

1057
01:12:01,042 --> 01:12:02,417
我还行
I'm fine.

1058
01:12:04,375 --> 01:12:07,083
我意思是，我有点……
I mean, there are things I've kind of,

1059
01:12:07,167 --> 01:12:10,208
你知道，选择对我来说……
you know, opted out of I guess.

1060
01:12:13,750 --> 01:12:16,292
不，我跟你还不一样
No, I'm not like you like that.

1061
01:12:16,375 --> 01:12:18,375
我不能……
I don't...

1062
01:12:19,042 --> 01:12:20,083
亚当？
Adam?

1063
01:12:20,208 --> 01:12:21,292
啊
Yeah.

1064
01:12:22,875 --> 01:12:25,208
你的生活还要继续
You've got to get in the game.

1065
01:12:28,375 --> 01:12:30,375
所以好好想想
So have a think.

1066
01:12:31,375 --> 01:12:35,542
你将来想干吗？你的梦想是什么？
What are your hopes,your dreams?

1067
01:12:39,250 --> 01:12:40,417
现在就说？
Right now?

1068
01:12:41,125 --> 01:12:42,292
对
Yeah.

1069
01:12:51,583 --> 01:12:53,708
松开我的手，松开
Let go of my hand. Let go of my hand.

1070
01:12:53,750 --> 01:12:55,250
我会松开的
I'll wipe out.

1071
01:12:55,333 --> 01:12:56,875
好吧，我会在你周围看着的
Yeah, but I'll be miles away.

1072
01:12:58,208 --> 01:13:00,875
来吧，自己试试，身体前倾往前滑就行了
Go on, all the way across. Just lean forward and run.

1073
01:13:00,917 --> 01:13:02,542
你能行的 
You can do it.

1074
01:13:03,208 --> 01:13:04,792
前倾往前走，明白了
Lean and run, got it.

1075
01:13:07,542 --> 01:13:10,292
滑起来！泰萨·斯科特来啦！
Get in! Tessa Scott is in the house!

1076
01:13:14,458 --> 01:13:15,458
卡尔，怎么停下来啊？
Cal, how do you stop?

1077
01:13:15,542 --> 01:13:16,542
撞墙
Use the wall.

1078
01:13:16,625 --> 01:13:18,417
卡尔！-扶墙！
Cal! -Use the wall!

1079
01:13:21,208 --> 01:13:22,375
嘿，宝贝
Hi, babe.

1080
01:13:23,042 --> 01:13:24,292
嘿
Hey.

1081
01:13:27,792 --> 01:13:29,375
你滑得不错
You looked good out there.

1082
01:13:29,875 --> 01:13:32,958
我老摔跤，现在屁股还疼呢
I kept falling down.My bum hurts.

1083
01:13:33,750 --> 01:13:36,083
你应该弄点冰冷敷一下
You should put some ice on it.

1084
01:13:42,208 --> 01:13:43,583
我想把孩子生下来
I'm keeping the baby.

1085
01:13:48,375 --> 01:13:49,583
真的？
Really?

1086
01:13:51,208 --> 01:13:53,708
对呀，生下来
Yeah. Yes.

1087
01:13:55,875 --> 01:13:59,250
是个女孩，我将有个女儿了
It's a girl. I'm having a girl.

1088
01:14:01,708 --> 01:14:04,083
我给她起了个名字叫劳伦
And I'm gonna call her Lauren.

1089
01:14:05,208 --> 01:14:06,708
我想要这个孩子
That's what I'm gonna do.

1090
01:14:07,875 --> 01:14:09,708
你生的时候我想去看看
I want to be there.

1091
01:14:11,250 --> 01:14:12,500
你要是不想让我进产房
If you don't want me in the birth,

1092
01:14:12,542 --> 01:14:14,292
我就在外边，等你生完了我再看
then I can sit outside and come in afterwards.

1093
01:14:18,083 --> 01:14:19,458
我想当世界上第一个
I want to be one of the first people

1094
01:14:19,542 --> 01:14:21,542
抱你孩子的人
in the world to ever hold your baby.

1095
01:14:25,875 --> 01:14:27,750
还有五个月才生呢
It's five months away.

1096
01:14:28,750 --> 01:14:31,125
这不就有目标了么
Then it's something to aim for.

1097
01:15:02,375 --> 01:15:05,083
你看，很多人觉得下雪很美
You see, some people would find this beautiful.

1098
01:15:05,208 --> 01:15:07,542
但是在我看来，这就是在屠杀我那些可怜的蔬菜
But all I can think is, it's killing my poor vegetables.

1099
01:15:10,875 --> 01:15:12,750
嘿，想什么呢，泰丝？
Hey, what's up, Tess?

1100
01:15:14,208 --> 01:15:17,417
我并不满足，对于我们，和这些美景
It's not enough. Us. This.

1101
01:15:18,417 --> 01:15:19,958
你的意思是？
How do you mean?

1102
01:15:20,750 --> 01:15:23,583
跟我在一起，和我一起住之类的
Stay with me. Stay the nights.

1103
01:15:26,250 --> 01:15:28,625
你想让我做什么，泰丝？
What do you want from me, Tess?

1104
01:15:29,250 --> 01:15:35,417
晚上，一起睡觉，早上一块起床，一起吃早饭
Nighttime. Sleeping together.Waking up together. Breakfast.

1105
01:15:37,625 --> 01:15:39,708
你真正想要的是什么？
What do you really want?

1106
01:15:44,375 --> 01:15:46,125
我想让你在黑暗里陪着我
I want you to be with me in the dark.

1107
01:15:48,542 --> 01:15:50,042
抱着我
To hold me.

1108
01:15:51,583 --> 01:15:53,375
一直爱我
To keep loving me.

1109
01:15:56,958 --> 01:15:59,250
在我害怕的时候安慰我
To help me when I get scared.

1110
