Your immune system is in collapse.

1206
01:22:19,250 --> 01:22:21,583
癌细胞已经扩散到全身了
The cancer is now everywhere.

1207
01:22:25,125 --> 01:22:27,250
我还有多长时间？
How much longer do I have?

1208
01:22:28,625 --> 01:22:30,917
我不想预测这个时间
I don't want to be drawn into time scales.

1209
01:22:32,875 --> 01:22:34,875
你说错了我不会告你的
I won't sue you if you're wrong.

1210
